---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Support — Visupair" description="Get help with your orders, products, and services. Access our FAQ and contact our support team.">
  <div class="support-layout">

    <!-- Left Block: FAQ Section -->
    <div class="support-faq-side">
      <div class="support-header">
        <h1 class="support-title">How can we help?</h1>
        <p class="support-subtitle">
          Find answers to common questions or reach out to our support team.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="support-faq-list">

        <div class="support-faq-panel">
          <button type="button" class="support-faq-item" data-faq="1" aria-expanded="false" id="sfaq-trigger-1" aria-controls="sfaq-answer-1">
            <span class="support-faq-number" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
            <h3 class="support-faq-question">Who is VisuPair?</h3>
            <div class="support-faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="support-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <polyline points="6,15 12,9 18,15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </button>
          <div class="support-faq-answer" data-faq="1" id="sfaq-answer-1" role="region" aria-labelledby="sfaq-trigger-1" aria-hidden="true">
            <p>We're Gul and Vali, two artists creating unique designs, fashion, 3D models, and digital art. We sell our work directly to you with no middlemen, combining our talents and visions into exceptional creations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-faq-panel">
          <button type="button" class="support-faq-item" data-faq="2" aria-expanded="false" id="sfaq-trigger-2" aria-controls="sfaq-answer-2">
            <span class="support-faq-number" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
            <h3 class="support-faq-question">What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
            <div class="support-faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="support-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <polyline points="6,15 12,9 18,15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </button>
          <div class="support-faq-answer" data-faq="2" id="sfaq-answer-2" role="region" aria-labelledby="sfaq-trigger-2" aria-hidden="true">
            <p>We accept all major credit and debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express, etc.) through Stripe secure checkout. Your payment data is encrypted with industry-standard security protocols, and we never store your card details on our servers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-faq-panel">
          <button type="button" class="support-faq-item" data-faq="3" aria-expanded="false" id="sfaq-trigger-3" aria-controls="sfaq-answer-3">
            <span class="support-faq-number" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
            <h3 class="support-faq-question">What's the difference between physical and digital products?</h3>
            <div class="support-faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="support-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <polyline points="6,15 12,9 18,15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </button>
          <div class="support-faq-answer" data-faq="3" id="sfaq-answer-3" role="region" aria-labelledby="sfaq-trigger-3" aria-hidden="true">
            <p>Physical products (hoodies, belts, paintings) are handmade and shipped to your address. Digital products (3D models, pattern files) are downloaded instantly after purchase and available in your account anytime.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-faq-panel">
          <button type="button" class="support-faq-item" data-faq="4" aria-expanded="false" id="sfaq-trigger-4" aria-controls="sfaq-answer-4">
            <span class="support-faq-number" aria-hidden="true">04</span>
            <h3 class="support-faq-question">How many revisions are included with services?</h3>
            <div class="support-faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="support-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <polyline points="6,15 12,9 18,15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </button>
          <div class="support-faq-answer" data-faq="4" id="sfaq-answer-4" role="region" aria-labelledby="sfaq-trigger-4" aria-hidden="true">
            <p>Revision rounds vary by service tier. Basic packages include 2 revisions, Standard includes 4 revisions, and Premium packages include unlimited revisions within scope. Check the specific service page for detailed information.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-faq-panel">
          <button type="button" class="support-faq-item" data-faq="5" aria-expanded="false" id="sfaq-trigger-5" aria-controls="sfaq-answer-5">
            <span class="support-faq-number" aria-hidden="true">05</span>
            <h3 class="support-faq-question">How do I track my order?</h3>
            <div class="support-faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="support-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <polyline points="6,15 12,9 18,15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </button>
          <div class="support-faq-answer" data-faq="5" id="sfaq-answer-5" role="region" aria-labelledby="sfaq-trigger-5" aria-hidden="true">
            <p>Log into your account and go to "Purchases" to view your order status, tracking number, estimated delivery date, and courier contact information. You'll also receive tracking updates via email.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-faq-panel">
          <button type="button" class="support-faq-item" data-faq="6" aria-expanded="false" id="sfaq-trigger-6" aria-controls="sfaq-answer-6">
            <span class="support-faq-number" aria-hidden="true">06</span>
            <h3 class="support-faq-question">What do you do if a product is out of stock?</h3>
            <div class="support-faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="support-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <polyline points="6,15 12,9 18,15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </button>
          <div class="support-faq-answer" data-faq="6" id="sfaq-answer-6" role="region" aria-labelledby="sfaq-trigger-6" aria-hidden="true">
            <p>When a product is sold out, you'll see a "Notify Me When Available" button instead of the Buy Now option. Simply enter your email address, and we'll send you a notification as soon as we restock it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-faq-panel">
          <button type="button" class="support-faq-item" data-faq="7" aria-expanded="false" id="sfaq-trigger-7" aria-controls="sfaq-answer-7">
            <span class="support-faq-number" aria-hidden="true">07</span>
            <h3 class="support-faq-question">Can I return or refund my order?</h3>
            <div class="support-faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="support-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <polyline points="6,15 12,9 18,15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </button>
          <div class="support-faq-answer" data-faq="7" id="sfaq-answer-7" role="region" aria-labelledby="sfaq-trigger-7" aria-hidden="true">
            <p>Refund eligibility depends on the product type and condition. Please refer to our Refund Policy for detailed information about eligibility timelines and refund processing. Contact us at info@visupair.com for personalized assistance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-faq-panel">
          <button type="button" class="support-faq-item" data-faq="8" aria-expanded="false" id="sfaq-trigger-8" aria-controls="sfaq-answer-8">
            <span class="support-faq-number" aria-hidden="true">08</span>
            <h3 class="support-faq-question">How do I contact support?</h3>
            <div class="support-faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="support-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <polyline points="6,15 12,9 18,15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </button>
          <div class="support-faq-answer" data-faq="8" id="sfaq-answer-8" role="region" aria-labelledby="sfaq-trigger-8" aria-hidden="true">
            <p>We're here to help! Reach us through Email: info@visupair.com or Phone: +48 539 818 790. We aim to respond to all inquiries within 24 hours.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Block: Contact Form -->
    <div class="support-form-side">
      <h2 class="support-form-heading">Still need help?</h2>

      <div class="support-direct-links">
        <a href="mailto:info@visupair.com" class="support-direct-link-btn">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
          </svg>
          info@visupair.com
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+48539818790" class="support-direct-link-btn">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.12 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path>
          </svg>
          +48 539 818 790
        </a>
      </div>

      <form class="support-form" id="support-form">
        <div class="support-form-row">
          <div class="support-form-group">
            <label class="support-form-label" for="firstName">First Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" class="support-form-input" placeholder="John" required />
          </div>
          <div class="support-form-group">
            <label class="support-form-label" for="lastName">Last Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" class="support-form-input" placeholder="Doe" required />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-form-group">
          <label class="support-form-label" for="email">Email Address</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="support-form-input" placeholder="john@company.com" required />
        </div>

        <div class="support-form-group">
          <label class="support-form-label" for="subject">Subject</label>
          <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" class="support-form-input" placeholder="How can we help?" required />
        </div>

        <div class="support-form-group">
          <label class="support-form-label" for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" class="support-form-input" placeholder="Describe your issue or question..." required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div>
          <button type="submit" class="support-btn-submit" id="support-submit-btn">
            <span class="support-btn-text">Send Message</span>
            <svg class="support-btn-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
              <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="support-privacy-text">
            By submitting this form, you agree to our <a href="/legal/privacy-policy">privacy policy</a>.
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>

      <div id="support-success-message" class="support-success-state" style="display: none;">
        <div class="support-success-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
            <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Message Sent!</h3>
        <p>Thanks for reaching out. We've received your message and will get back to you shortly.</p>
        <button id="support-send-another" class="support-btn-outline">Send Another</button>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .support-layout {
    display: flex;
    width: calc(100% - 24px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    gap: 12px;
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════
     LEFT: FAQ
     ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
  .support-faq-side {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.02), var(--shadow-island);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-faq-side {
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.2), var(--shadow-island);
  }

  .support-header {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .support-title {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--foreground);
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-title { color: #ffffff; }

  .support-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(14px, 1.2vw, 16px);
    color: var(--foreground);
    opacity: 0.65;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-subtitle { color: #e9e8ff; }

  /* List of panels */
  .support-faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  /* Panel card */
  .support-faq-panel {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 88%, transparent);
    overflow: hidden;
    isolation: isolate;
    transition: border-color 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  }

  .support-faq-panel:has(.support-faq-item[aria-expanded="true"]) {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-violet) 35%, var(--border-subtle));
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-violet) 12%, transparent);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-faq-panel {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 92%, #0c0b14 8%);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-faq-panel:has(.support-faq-item[aria-expanded="true"]) {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 28px rgba(132, 128, 255, 0.18);
  }

  /* Trigger row */
  .support-faq-item {
    all: unset;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px 18px;
    width: 100%;
    padding: clamp(15px, 2vw, 20px) clamp(16px, 2.2vw, 22px);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
  }

  .support-faq-item:hover {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-hover) 65%, transparent);
  }

  .support-faq-item:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--brand-violet);
    outline-offset: -2px;
  }

  /* Number pill */
  .support-faq-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    padding: 0 0.35rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--brand-violet);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-violet) 14%, transparent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* Question text */
  .support-faq-question {
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1vw, 15px);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--foreground);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    text-align: left;
    word-break: break-word;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-faq-question { color: #ffffff; }

  /* Toggle circle */
  .support-faq-toggle {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: 999px;
    line-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: var(--brand-violet);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-violet) 12%, transparent);
    transition: background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .support-faq-item:hover .support-faq-toggle {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-violet) 20%, transparent);
  }

  .support-faq-chevron {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    display: block;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transform-origin: 50% 50%;
    transform: rotate(0deg);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.3, 0.64, 1);
  }

  .support-faq-item[aria-expanded="true"] .support-faq-toggle {
    color: #fff;
    background: var(--brand-violet);
  }

  .support-faq-item[aria-expanded="true"] .support-faq-chevron {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  /* Answer panel */
  .support-faq-answer {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), padding 0.35s ease;
    padding: 0 clamp(16px, 2.2vw, 22px);
    margin: 0;
    border: none;
  }

  .support-faq-answer.open {
    position: relative;
    max-height: min(70vh, 760px);
    padding: 0 clamp(16px, 2.2vw, 22px) clamp(14px, 1.8vw, 18px);
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .support-faq-answer.open::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: clamp(16px, 2.2vw, 22px);
    right: clamp(16px, 2.2vw, 22px);
    top: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--border-subtle) 70%, var(--surface));
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .support-faq-answer p {
    font-size: clamp(13px, 0.95vw, 15px);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--foreground);
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: clamp(12px, 1.5vw, 16px);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-faq-answer p { color: #e9e8ff; }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════
     RIGHT: FORM  (matches contact.astro)
     ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
  .support-form-side {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.02), var(--shadow-island);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-form-side {
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.2), var(--shadow-island);
  }

  .support-form-heading {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--foreground);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-form-heading { color: #ffffff; }

  /* Direct contact links — side by side like contact.astro */
  .support-direct-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .support-direct-link-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--surface-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 18px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--foreground);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .support-direct-link-btn:hover {
    border-color: var(--brand-violet);
    color: var(--brand-violet);
    background: rgba(132, 128, 255, 0.05);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Form */
  .support-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .support-form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .support-form-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .support-form-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    opacity: 0.9;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .support-form-label { color: #e9e8ff; }

  .support-form-input {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--surface-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 14px 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--foreground);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .support-form-input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--brand-violet);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(132, 128, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .support-form-input::placeholder { opacity: 0.4; }

  textarea.support-form-input {
    min-height: 140px;
    resize: vertical;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
  }

  /* Submit button — matches contact.astro .btn-submit */
  .support-btn-submit {
    background: rgba(132, 128, 255, 0.05);
    color: var(--brand-violet);
    border: 1px solid var(--brand-violet);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 8px;
    width: 100%;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
  }

  .support-btn-submit:hover {
    background: var(--brand-violet);
    color: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(132, 128, 255, 0.25);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .support-btn-submit:disabled {
    opacity: 0.7;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    transform: none;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .support-privacy-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.5;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .support-privacy-text a {
    color: var(--foreground);
    text-decoration: underline;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .support-privacy-text a:hover { opacity: 1; }

  /* Success state */
  .support-success-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 0;
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out;
  }

  .support-success-state h3 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .support-success-state p {
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .support-success-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: var(--brand-lime);
    color: var(--brand-dark-navy);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
  }

  .support-success-icon svg {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
  }

  .support-btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    color: var(--foreground);
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
  }

  .support-btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--brand-violet);
    color: var(--brand-violet);
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════
     RESPONSIVE
     ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .support-layout {
      gap: 16px;
      width: calc(100% - 32px);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .support-layout {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
      width: calc(100% - 32px);
    }

    .support-faq-side,
    .support-form-side {
      padding: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);
    }

    .support-title {
      font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px);
    }

    .support-form-heading {
      font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 32px);
    }

    .support-form-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .support-layout {
      width: 100%;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .support-faq-side,
    .support-form-side {
      padding: 20px 16px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    }

